title: He
description: There was nothing.  No feeling.  No numbness.  No pain.  That could describe.   He went to find the truth.  And she stole me.  I hope she was worth it.   There was nothing.  No words.  No fists.  No problems.  I’m never good enough.  I hope this hell is worth it. Because she isn’t and neither am I.  But he damn sure is.
author: Kailee Reese Samuels
